headline: Raymond James To Welcome New $605 Million Program with Texas Community Bank
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., July 31, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Raymond James Financial Institutions Division (FID) announced today that Texas Community Bank (TCB) has selected the firm’s platform to enhance its financial planning and advisory offering, according to Stephen Kruchten, president of FID. With this new alignment, TCB Investments will provide clients with investment and wealth management services through Raymond James Financial Services.
